## On-page SEO Checklist

1. Title tag: keyword + city + brand (<=60 chars)
2. Meta description: CTA + uniqueness (<=155 chars)
3. H1: one per page, contains target keyword
4. Alt texts: descriptive, with keywords (NGG alttext)
5. Internal links: >=3 per page, keyword-rich anchors
6. Schema.org: JSON-LD in header

## Meta Description Template

```
/seo-smm meta [URL] [ET/RU]
-> 155-160 chars, with CTA and keywords
```

