## Distilled 2026-03-24

### Re-Indexing Protocol

- **Dual-channel submission** for fastest coverage: <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->
  - **IndexNow API** → instant submission to Bing and Yandex (single API call, no OAuth)
  - **Google Search Console** → manual URL inspection + "Request Indexing" for Google coverage
- **Token management**: Google OAuth tokens expire in approximately 1 week–30 days depending on consent screen configuration — document token creation date and set calendar reminder for refresh. <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->
- Use after: new page publish, SEO metadata update, hreflang change, schema markup change. <!-- decay:2026-03-24 tier:cold rel:0.385 -->

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-24-oRnmHNVPrZ4_2026-03-24-18-52.md -->

