### PATTERN — Система обучения AI на личном стиле

• Export 30-50 posts → build Obsidian graph → train AI agent on style patterns
• After 5-7 corrections, AI achieves 80%+ style accuracy
• Document each correction as permanent rule for agent

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### PATTERN — Итеративное улучшение качества

• Request 3 post variants from AI, select best
• Provide specific feedback with reasons ("fewer English words", "personal tone")
• Agent saves patterns as rules; max accuracy by 10th post

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### GOTCHA — Проблемы стандартного подхода

• Generic prompts produce template content without individuality
• Copying copywriter skills fails; need brand voice first (10-15 manual posts)
• First 5-10 AI posts require manual correction

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### PATTERN — Применение на разных платформах

• Train AI on one platform (Telegram) → extract patterns for others (Threads, Instagram, TikTok)
• Use same Obsidian knowledge base; adapt format, preserve brand voice

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### PATTERN — Структура хранения контента

• Organize Obsidian by platform (Telegram, Instagram, Threads, TikTok)
• Each post = separate Markdown file with metadata

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### PATTERN — Граф связей для контекстного поиска

• AI creates link system by keywords → enables contextual search without full archive scan
• Saves tokens; agent accesses only relevant notes
• Separate text and video content for precise matching

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### PATTERN — Автоматическое обогащение базы

• Send screenshot/text to AI → auto-adds post to Obsidian with metadata
• After 3-7 days add reaction metrics
• AI learns to identify successful content types via metrics

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### PATTERN — Процесс экспорта контента

• Open channel in Telegram Desktop → Menu → Export chat history
• Format: JSON, all messages from beginning
• Pass JSON file to AI agent for parsing

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### GOTCHA — Альтернативное использование

Can export other users' Telegram channels if you lack own brand voice; create content based on their style

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### PATTERN — Работа с AI-агентом

• Pass JSON export to AI → parse content → place in Obsidian
• Auto-create knowledge graph
• Agent handles parsing/saving without intervention

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### PATTERN — Будущая автоматизация мониторинга

Plan: embed AI agent in Telegram channel for auto-tracking reactions, updating metrics in real-time, analyzing effectiveness without manual input

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### FACT — Целевая аудитория

Content creators, bloggers, Telegram channel owners, AI users for social media content generation

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### PATTERN — Стартовая последовательность

Stage 1: Download materials, define brand voice (or write 15 posts), install tools
Stage 2: Export Telegram JSON, create Obsidian folder structure, send to AI
Stage 3-5: AI builds files + graph, request 3 variants, iterate, scale to other platforms

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### PATTERN — Экономия ресурсов

• Tokens: graph loads only relevant content, not entire archive
• Time: automate parsing, saving, structuring
• Quality: AI learns from success metrics (likes, views, comments)

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### GOTCHA — Необходимые условия успеха

✓ Clear brand voice (or willingness to develop one) ✓ Min 30-50 content samples ✓ 5-10 feedback iterations ✓ Regular reaction metrics; ✗ Without these = template content only

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### PATTERN — Обучение через примеры

Show real examples of your content, not copywriter skills. Use concrete examples + patterns, not generic instructions. Continuous learning via feedback, not one-time setup.

<!-- source: YT-2026-03-29-56KZASHPkV8_2026-03-29.md -->

### GOTCHA — Финальное предупреждение

System reproduces existing brand voice; does not create one. Requires pre-existing voice to work effectively.

